00139             entries->GetData(index, 0, entry.id);

00198 ParameterNameValueTypeList CHPQuantificationDetectionData::GetAlgParams()
00199 {
00200         ParameterNameValueTypeList nvt;
00201         ParameterNameValueTypeIt begin, end;
00202         ParameterNameValueType param;
00203 
00204         genericData.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->GetNameValIterators(begin, end);
00205         while(begin != end)
00206         {
00207                 std::wstring key = begin->GetName();
00208                 if(key.compare(0, ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S.size(),ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S) == 0)
00209                 {
00210                         param = *begin;
00211                         key.erase(0, ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S.size());
00212                         param.SetName(key);
00213                         nvt.push_back(param);
00214                 }
00215                 begin++;
00216         }
00217         return nvt;
